snippet.title: Miniatures - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Miniatures is a carefully curated collection of four handcrafted adventures about childhood, where imagination and reality merge with darker undercurrents of loneliness, mystery and magic.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2428840/Miniatures/

Miniatures will be released on Steam, App Store, and Nintendo eShop on the 14th of November💛
